name: Ripple Signals Rapid Expansion With XRP and RLUSD Set to Boost Institutional Collateral
description: The Canine-Hierophant seals the pact. Through solemn gesture, the Sentinels drink the electrified blood—a volumetric current of cyan-magenta data, binding them in collateral fusion. The grit of the old world accepts the liquid pulse of the new, generating kinetic market divinity.
